  {
    "skill": "writing",
    "module": "academic",
    "title": "IELTS Writing Task 1: Employment by Sector Table",
    "task": 1,
    "topic_tags": [
      "work",
      "economy"
    ],
    "essay_type": "table",
    "difficulty": "medium",
    "prompt_html": "<p>The table below shows the percentage of the workforce employed in four sectors of one country’s economy in 2000, 2010 and 2020. Summarise the information by selecting and reporting the main features, and make comparisons where relevant.</p><div style=\"overflow-x:auto\"><table style=\"border-collapse:collapse;width:100%;max-width:560px;margin:12px auto 0;font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,sans-serif;font-size:13px\"><caption style=\"caption-side:top;font-weight:700;color:#0A2540;padding-bottom:8px;font-size:14px\">Employment by sector, 2000–2020 (% of the workforce)</caption><thead><tr><th style=\"border:1px solid #cbd5e1;padding:8px 10px;text-align:left;background:#f1f5f9\">Sector</th><th style=\"border:1px solid #cbd5e1;padding:8px 10px;text-align:right;background:#f1f5f9\">2000</th><th style=\"border:1px solid #cbd5e1;padding:8px 10px;text-align:right;background:#f1f5f9\">2010</th><th style=\"border:1px solid #cbd5e1;padding:8px 10px;text-align:right;background:#f1f5f9\">2020</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #cbd5e1;padding:8px 10px;text-align:left\">Agriculture</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #cbd5e1;padding:8px 10px;text-align:right\">12</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #cbd5e1;padding:8px 10px;text-align:right\">8</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #cbd5e1;padding:8px 10px;text-align:right\">5</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #cbd5e1;padding:8px 10px;text-align:left\">Manufacturing</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #cbd5e1;padding:8px 10px;text-align:right\">30</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #cbd5e1;padding:8px 10px;text-align:right\">24</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #cbd5e1;padding:8px 10px;text-align:right\">18</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #cbd5e1;padding:8px 10px;text-align:left\">Services</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #cbd5e1;padding:8px 10px;text-align:right\">48</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #cbd5e1;padding:8px 10px;text-align:right\">58</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #cbd5e1;padding:8px 10px;text-align:right\">67</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #cbd5e1;padding:8px 10px;text-align:left\">Construction</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #cbd5e1;padding:8px 10px;text-align:right\">10</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #cbd5e1;padding:8px 10px;text-align:right\">10</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #cbd5e1;padding:8px 10px;text-align:right\">10</td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>Write at least 150 words.</p>",
