  },
  {
    "skill": "writing",
    "module": "academic",
    "title": "IELTS Writing Task 1: How Glass Bottles Are Recycled Process Diagram",
    "task": 1,
    "topic_tags": [
      "environment",
      "science"
    ],
    "essay_type": "process diagram",
    "difficulty": "hard",
    "prompt_html": "<p>The diagram below illustrates the process by which used glass bottles are recycled into new ones. Summarise the information by selecting and reporting the main features, and make comparisons where relevant.</p><svg viewBox=\"0 0 700 430\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Process diagram showing how glass bottles are recycled\" style=\"display:block;width:100%;height:auto;max-width:700px;margin:12px auto 0\"><rect width=\"700\" height=\"430\" fill=\"#ffffff\"/><text x=\"350\" y=\"34\" font-family=\"system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,sans-serif\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"700\" fill=\"#0A2540\" text-anchor=\"middle\">How glass bottles are recycled</text><defs><marker id=\"wr2arrow\" markerWidth=\"9\" markerHeight=\"9\" refX=\"7\" refY=\"4.5\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L9,4.5 L0,9 z\" fill=\"#64748b\"/></marker></defs><rect x=\"40\" y=\"70\" width=\"180\" height=\"84\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#f8fafc\" stroke=\"#94a3b8\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><circle cx=\"58\" cy=\"88\" r=\"12\" fill=\"#0A2540\"/><text x=\"58\" y=\"92\" font-family=\"system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,sans-serif\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"700\" fill=\"#ffffff\" text-anchor=\"middle\">1</text><text x=\"130\" y=\"109\" font-family=\"system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,sans-serif\" font-size=\"12.5\" fill=\"#334155\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Used bottles collected</text><text x=\"130\" y=\"125\" font-family=\"system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,sans-serif\" font-size=\"12.5\" fill=\"#334155\" text-anchor=\"middle\">from homes and bottle</text><text x=\"130\" y=\"141\" font-family=\"system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,sans-serif\" font-size=\"12.5\" fill=\"#334155\" text-anchor=\"middle\">banks</text><rect x=\"260\" y=\"70\" width=\"180\" height=\"84\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#f8fafc\" stroke=\"#94a3b8\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><circle cx=\"278\" cy=\"88\" r=\"12\" fill=\"#0A2540\"/><text x=\"278\" y=\"92\" font-family=\"system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,sans-serif\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"700\" fill=\"#ffffff\" text-anchor=\"middle\">2</text><text x=\"350\" y=\"117\" font-family=\"system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,sans-serif\" font-size=\"12.5\" fill=\"#334155\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Bottles sorted by</text><text x=\"350\" y=\"133\" font-family=\"system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,sans-serif\" font-size=\"12.5\" fill=\"#334155\" text-anchor=\"middle\">colour and washed</text><rect x=\"480\" y=\"70\" width=\"180\" height=\"84\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#f8fafc\" stroke=\"#94a3b8\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><circle cx=\"498\" cy=\"88\" r=\"12\" fill=\"#0A2540\"/><text x=\"498\" y=\"92\" font-family=\"system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,sans-serif\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"700\" fill=\"#ffffff\" text-anchor=\"middle\">3</text><text x=\"570\" y=\"109\" font-family=\"system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,sans-serif\" font-size=\"12.5\" fill=\"#334155\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Clean glass crushed</text><text x=\"570\" y=\"125\" font-family=\"system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,sans-serif\" font-size=\"12.5\" fill=\"#334155\" text-anchor=\"middle\">into small pieces</text><text x=\"570\" y=\"141\" font-family=\"system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,sans-serif\" font-size=\"12.5\" fill=\"#334155\" text-anchor=\"middle\">called cullet</text><rect x=\"480\" y=\"250\" width=\"180\" height=\"84\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#f8fafc\" stroke=\"#94a3b8\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><circle cx=\"498\" cy=\"268\" r=\"12\" fill=\"#0A2540\"/><text x=\"498\" y=\"272\" font-family=\"system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,sans-serif\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"700\" fill=\"#ffffff\" text-anchor=\"middle\">4</text><text x=\"570\" y=\"289\" font-family=\"system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,sans-serif\" font-size=\"12.5\" fill=\"#334155\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Cullet melted in a</text><text x=\"570\" y=\"305\" font-family=\"system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,sans-serif\" font-size=\"12.5\" fill=\"#334155\" text-anchor=\"middle\">furnace at high</text><text x=\"570\" y=\"321\" font-family=\"system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,sans-serif\" font-size=\"12.5\" fill=\"#334155\" text-anchor=\"middle\">temperature</text><rect x=\"260\" y=\"250\" width=\"180\" height=\"84\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#f8fafc\" stroke=\"#94a3b8\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><circle cx=\"278\" cy=\"268\" r=\"12\" fill=\"#0A2540\"/><text x=\"278\" y=\"272\" font-family=\"system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,sans-serif\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"700\" fill=\"#ffffff\" text-anchor=\"middle\">5</text><text x=\"350\" y=\"289\" font-family=\"system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,sans-serif\" font-size=\"12.5\" fill=\"#334155\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Molten glass moulded</text><text x=\"350\" y=\"305\" font-family=\"system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,sans-serif\" font-size=\"12.5\" fill=\"#334155\" text-anchor=\"middle\">into new bottles and</text><text x=\"350\" y=\"321\" font-family=\"system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,sans-serif\" font-size=\"12.5\" fill=\"#334155\" text-anchor=\"middle\">cooled</text><rect x=\"40\" y=\"250\" width=\"180\" height=\"84\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#f8fafc\" stroke=\"#94a3b8\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><circle cx=\"58\" cy=\"268\" r=\"12\" fill=\"#0A2540\"/><text x=\"58\" y=\"272\" font-family=\"system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,sans-serif\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"700\" fill=\"#ffffff\" text-anchor=\"middle\">6</text><text x=\"130\" y=\"297\" font-family=\"system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,sans-serif\" font-size=\"12.5\" fill=\"#334155\" text-anchor=\"middle\">New bottles filled and</text><text x=\"130\" y=\"313\" font-family=\"system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,sans-serif\" font-size=\"12.5\" fill=\"#334155\" text-anchor=\"middle\">delivered to shops</text><line x1=\"220\" y1=\"112\" x2=\"260\" y2=\"112\" stroke=\"#64748b\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" marker-end=\"url(#wr2arrow)\"/><line x1=\"440\" y1=\"112\" x2=\"480\" y2=\"112\" stroke=\"#64748b\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" marker-end=\"url(#wr2arrow)\"/><line x1=\"570\" y1=\"154\" x2=\"570\" y2=\"250\" stroke=\"#64748b\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" marker-end=\"url(#wr2arrow)\"/><line x1=\"480\" y1=\"292\" x2=\"440\" y2=\"292\" stroke=\"#64748b\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" marker-end=\"url(#wr2arrow)\"/><line x1=\"260\" y1=\"292\" x2=\"220\" y2=\"292\" stroke=\"#64748b\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" marker-end=\"url(#wr2arrow)\"/></svg><p>Write at least 150 words.</p>",
